summary:
Over 8 years teaching experience with nonnative speakers specialising  in Business and Academic English. 

Past students have successfully achieved high grades in TOFEL and in Cambridge certification examinations.

Previous clients (through Business Talen Rotterdam) include: HBU, Robeco, Shell, Royal Haskoning and RSM.

Specialties: Customer service and complaints handling. Staff training and education. Communication and presentation. Skills building specialist. Effective Business English trainer.
